title: Team - California Berry Cultivars

headings.text: The California Berry Cultivars team consists of a mix of veterans and the next generation of strawberry cultivar developers and researchers.

paragraphs: They have a collective 100+ years of experience in the strawberry industry and are committed to providing strawberry growers with the quality strawberries they want and need. The significant amount of experience within the CBC team is well-suited to conduct strawberry research in order to further the knowledge base required by the strawberry industry to protect and promote a quality, high-yielding, consumer-desirable product under the ever changing conditions of the field and market place.
rawHtml:
The California Berry Cultivars team consists of a mix of veterans and the next generation of strawberry cultivar developers and researchers.

They have a collective 100+ years of experience in the strawberry industry and are committed to providing strawberry growers with the quality strawberries they want and need. The significant amount of experience within the CBC team is well-suited to conduct strawberry research in order to further the knowledge base required by the strawberry industry to protect and promote a quality, high-yielding, consumer-desirable product under the ever changing conditions of the field and market place.
